  • Classes in it.polimi.travlendarplus.entities used by it.polimi.travlendarplus.entities 
    Class and Description
    EntityWithLongKey
    This JPA abstract class represent a generic JPA class that have a long primary key, it is to be implemented by all entities that must have such a key
    GenericEntity
    This is the main entity class, it is to be extended by all entity classes of Travlendar+ The class implements the Serializable interface, since is to be implemented by all entities classes
    GenericEntityTest 
    Location
    This JPA class represent a location ( geographic coordinates of a specific point on the earth surface)
    LocationId
    Support class used to provide a key to Location class, since JPA needs that a key is represented either by a primitive data type or by a class
    RSAEncryption
    This JPA class represent a RSA key pair, associated to a specific device in order to encrypt and decrypt sensible data sent through internet connectivity
    Timestamp
    This Embeddable class is used to provide the record of the time when the last update is performed to all JPA class that needs such functionality
    User
    This JPA class represent a Travlendar+ registered user
    UserDevice
    This JPA class represent a user device
    UserLocation
    This JPA class represent a preferred user location
